				<wikidot:authorName>shoofle</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>870919</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Honestly, this just didn't seem like a very good SCP to me. It's entertaining, sure, but it's also SCP troperiffic, and the main article is just too&#8230; silly. Why does it shoot mice? Mice are inherently funny creatures.<br /> The exploration log is decent, but it's also full of GRITTY MTF SAYING FUCK AND GETTING KILLED! WHOA which is awfully tired. And how many SCPs can we write which are Mysterious Facilities What As Have Shifting, Impossible Interiors? It's not even scary to me any more - just another shapeshifting maze. This SCP didn't hold together.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
